{"tid":1495161,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"監警會副主席：速龍小隊執勤時展示編號並不公平","createTime":"2019-08-22T02:59:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T08:12:50.000Z","uid":209024,"like":3,"dislike":52,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"9846dc03df64f56dfd03785c4a1065fd57dc312f","tid":1495161,"uid":209024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T02:59:37.000Z","msg":"張華峰稱市民毋須靠編號 應按事發地點等投訴速龍小隊<br />\n2019-08-22 HKT 10:49<br />\n 分享工具  facebook  twitter<br />\n監警會副主席張華峰在本台節目「千禧年代」說，一般警員巡邏時需要清晰展示警員編號，但認為速龍小隊是為了處理嚴重情況，而警員家屬資料隨時遭人放到網上，張華峰認為，速龍小隊執勤時展示包括警隊編號等所有資料並不公平，認為他們是在執行法律，應無後顧之憂。<br />\n<br />\n張華峰說，在處理騷動時，警方使用的武力是否過分，要視乎對方的反應如何，質疑當警方執行社會穩定的任務，是否要限制他們使用武力的程度，認為當時應由警員作判斷。<br />\n<br />\n張華峰在節目後表示，市民如要投訴速龍小隊，可不單靠其編號作投訴，亦可以按速龍小隊的行為、動作及個案發生的地點等作投訴依據。他並無直接回應如果速龍小隊無展示警員編號，會否削弱市民監察的權利，至於公眾找不到速龍小隊編號，張華峰說應由投訴警察課處理。<br />\n<br />\n監警會前委員梁繼昌表示，速龍小隊在前兩年都有展示警員編號，不明白其後無展示的原因，又質疑當局以速龍小隊衣服上無位置擺放編號的理據，建議把速龍小隊警員編號放在頭盔上，減少警民之間的猜疑。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1476065-20190822.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1476065-20190822.htm&d=MOEBQbH5BhSBv0g7AWUGIQPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=60900372\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1476065-20190822.htm&h=4394b0a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1476065-20190822.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1e4f12f7ac8fc9d33aa8f93f87b6e33fac7d3ed8","tid":1495161,"uid":281926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T03:00:29.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n香港人可攻可守，智勇雙全！<br />\n記住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>It&rsquo;s now or never</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>824 機場復活，WE WANT YOU，而家搭車犯法呀?</strong></span></span> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yrRtRqw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyrRtRqw.jpg&h=a938cd9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wTCkHxb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwTCkHxb.jpg&h=73ff0599&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/00prC5w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F00prC5w.jpg&h=ccabd632&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WJckHxb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWJckHxb.jpg&h=e84b0cd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x3bJFtJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx3bJFtJ.jpg&h=400310ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7mzORrS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7mzORrS.jpg&h=e1aa2d33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uvSwHez.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuvSwHez.png&h=660b03dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a27572f9221ac4f5bd288e4a7d2a7f1749940ac4","tid":1495161,"uid":40763,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T03:14:29.000Z","msg":"屌你老母支那同班撚樣搞亂哂香港<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港獨立</span>"},{"pid":"c6cfa975d5e84376f825332dd859511081d0c600","tid":1495161,"uid":92170,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T03:16:54.000Z","msg":"監警會可被起訴；<br />\n監警會不是政府的僱員或代理人，亦不享有政府的地位、豁免權或特權。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cvyoFit.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcvyoFit.png&h=f33fb384&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n監警條例亦訂明警務處處長為投訴定案，但無註明涉及投訴警務處處長，例如處長行為失當、作出不合法命令等，條例中並無列明相關機制，亦無任何獨立人仕授權處理涉及處長投訴，即係處長自己查自己。<br />\n<br />\n所有涉及處長投訴，除非成立由法官領導既獨立調查委員會處理，否則監警會係無辦法處理，亦無任何公信力。政府所講所有涉及警務投訴，都可由監警會處理其實並不正確，只要投訴對象係處長，監警會係廢既。<br />\n<br />\n另外民事起訴警方，係並不需要由警方作出調查，咁當然舉證難，入罪難，一齊研究。"},{"pid":"906c7f71d3145611eed6b9a6cf9a018e9eb6ac2b","tid":1495161,"uid":143321,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T03:16:58.000Z","msg":"佢講得啱呀<br />\n<br />\n所以我地唔到監警會<br />\n<br />\n堅持5 大訴求"},{"pid":"395694d121b8b1b25014e7bd695c50cae9bfe1b1","tid":1495161,"uid":197157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T03:18:11.000Z","msg":"所以咪有5大訴求囉<br />\n因為係人都知監警係廢"},{"pid":"c9e485d82b906b799accff01a8fde08af5a75140","tid":1495161,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T03:19:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a3e3a0df72c00e7903aba52d9b7cd49c681e595","tid":1495161,"uid":28168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T03:20:47.000Z","msg":"黑警抱起市民屌時 應無後顧之憂"},{"pid":"5e14737d2a44e93449d597012ef51704e3e2ccbd","tid":1495161,"uid":121580,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T03:21:55.000Z","msg":"監警會:我係無牙老虎,我係廢物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e96fd181f27d3adcf37358b2cb1e443cb5f1fedb","tid":1495161,"uid":55130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T03:22:04.000Z","msg":"你又槍又棍叫咩公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"969c7d6be559336dee915cf024dce94c4d153623","tid":1495161,"uid":160284,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T03:23:10.000Z","msg":"行得正企得正驚咩？"},{"pid":"dd3148f5fe32f6ada2d57bf254e5ea18e280c3d9","tid":1495161,"uid":243407,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T03:29:26.000Z","msg":"蓄生離隊偷走去強姦人點算<br />\n冇編號點知有冇人冒警<br />\n點追究"},{"pid":"1eab548ef820c377a55d8bc98eb3dfe06b65a19e","tid":1495161,"uid":121580,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T04:00:24.000Z","msg":"無後顧之憂?<br />\n你係跟據法律做野,<br />\n係光明正大既怕